name: Security Vulnerability
description: Report a security vulnerability responsibly
title: "[Security]: "
labels: ["security", "bug"]
type: bug
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        **IMPORTANT:** For serious security vulnerabilities, please **DO NOT** open a public issue. Instead, check our SECURITY.md for responsible disclosure instructions.

        This form is for non-critical security concerns that can be discussed publicly.

  - type: dropdown
    id: severity
    attributes:
      label: Severity
      description: How severe is this vulnerability?
      options:
        - Low - Minor security concern, limited impact
        - Medium - Moderate vulnerability with some impact
        - High - Serious vulnerability affecting security
        - Critical - Do not use this form, follow SECURITY.md instead
      default: 1
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: vulnerability-description
    attributes:
      label: Vulnerability description
      description: Describe the security issue
      placeholder: "Explain the vulnerability and why it's a security concern..."
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: affected-components
    attributes:
      label: Affected components
      description: Which parts of the code/project are affected?
      placeholder: |
        - Component/file: [description of vulnerability]
        - Dependency: [version or range]
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: reproduction
    attributes:
      label: How to reproduce / Proof of concept
      description: Steps to demonstrate the vulnerability (if applicable)
      placeholder: "Provide a minimal example or reproduction steps..."

  - type: textarea
    id: impact
    attributes:
      label: Potential impact
      description: What could an attacker do? Who is affected?
      placeholder: "Describe the potential consequences if this is exploited..."
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: suggested-fix
    attributes:
      label: Suggested mitigation
      description: How should this be fixed? (optional)
      placeholder: "Propose a solution or mitigation strategy..."

  - type: checkboxes
    id: checklist
    attributes:
      label: Pre-submission checklist
      options:
        - label: This is not a critical vulnerability (critical issues should use SECURITY.md)
          required: true
        - label: I have provided sufficient detail for understanding the issue
          required: true
        - label: I have described the potential impact
          required: true
